cdata.name: LocalCoinSwap
cdata.desc: LocalCoinSwap is a community-owned peer-to-peer (P2P) exchange for cryptocrurrencies and tokens. It allows users to exchange cryptos with several alternative payment methods while distributing 100% of its profits back to LCS token holders. The LCS token is an ERC20 token based on the Ethereum blockchain, allowing holders to receive part of the revenue generated by the P2P exchange, in accordance with the amount of tokens they hold.
